item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】WAV - Brit Smith - Karma's A Bitch [2024 Version] (WAV) [16bit / 44.1kHz]
item.description:
This is an unofficial mix of Jojo's "Karma", completely removing Jojo (as one should) from the song, and mixing Brit Smith's vocals into it. I never finished it and don't have the time to anymore, my goal was NOT to cut down Brit's vocals to fit the new instrumentation and arrangement, but instead change and extend the instrumental to fit all of Brit's vocal track.

Again, this is unfinished, the last chorus was cut short, and the mastering is shoddy so don't expect it to be perfect. Maybe one day I'll finish it, or someone likely did this already and it's somewhere on YouTube, idk.

Here ya go.
